beer.beer_description: ​Meet the Bookie. He will happily take your hard earn clams for the long shot, but if you want a sure thing, this brew is for you! Aromas of citrus and tropical fruits takes you back to summer holidays. A medium body with a hint of breadiness is back up with a flavoursome and firm bitterness. This beer is the real deal and provides all the action your taste buds need.
